org.glassfish.jersey.client.rx

Interface RxWebTarget<RX extends RxInvoker>

  • Type Parameters:
    RX - the concrete reactive invocation type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    javax.ws.rs.core.Configurable<javax.ws.rs.client.WebTarget>, javax.ws.rs.client.WebTarget

    public interface RxWebTarget<RX extends RxInvoker>
extends javax.ws.rs.client.WebTarget
    A reactive resource target identified by the resource URI.

    RxWebTarget extension overrides methods of JAX-RS client target to give user a way to access the reactive contracts.

    Since:
    2.13
    Author:
    Michal Gajdos, Marek Potociar (marek.potociar at oracle.com)
    See Also:
    WebTarget, RxInvoker
